            a
            ,
            b
            ∈
            A
          
          }
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle x_{\geq a}:=\left\{x_{b}:b\geq a,b\in A\right\}}
   for each 
  
    
      
        a
        ∈
        A
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle a\in A.}
   
If 
  
    
      
