   defined on 
  
    
      
        
          N
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbb {N} .}
  
The net is eventually in a subset 
  
    
      
        S
      
    
    {\displaystyle S}
   of 
  
    
      
        X
      
    
    {\displaystyle X}
   if there exists an 
  
    
      
